high_descs: Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the fireplace.
Pick up the leftmost glass vase off of the fireplace mantle.
Turn right and walk over to the end table to the left of the couch.
Put the glass vase on the end table.
Turn left and walk over to the fireplace.
Pick up the glass vase off of the fireplace mantle.
Turn around and walk over to the end table that is to the left of the couch.
Put the glass vase on top of the end table.
anns.task_desc: Move two glass vases onto the end table.

high_descs: move to the mantle in the middle of the windows
pick up a vase from the mantle
move to the end table to the left of the couch
put the vase on the end table
move to the mantle in the middle of the windows
pick up a vase from the mantle
move to the end table to the left of the couch
put the vase on the end table
anns.task_desc: Put two vases on a end table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the left side of the mantle of the fireplace.
Pick up the gray bowl on the mantle.
Go to the other side of the living room to the small black cabinet.
Place the bowl on the top of the cabinet.
Turn left to go to the right side of the mantle of the fire place.
Pick up the brown bowl on the mantle.
Turn around and go back to the small black cabinet.
Place the brown bowl to the left of the gray bowl.
anns.task_desc: Move the bowls from the mantle to the cabinet.
